      "span_text": "In this study, and for the first time to our knowledge, we report on the circularization and transfer into bacterial cells of YAC 37AB12, which contains an insert spanning the intact human CFTR locus plus additional 5 0 and 3 0 DNA. We have produced two versions of this circular BAC that differ in the 5 0 upstream DNA by about 25 kb."
